long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This NitroGAS Chrome Extension is a featured packed tool built by Bootstrapping Tools to help make writing code in Google Apps Script easier and faster. If you're familiar with our Youtube Channel, you know that we're big fans of creating custom solutions for Google Sheets, Docs, Slides, and more. NitroGAS was built to help us build scripts faster so we know that it'll help you as well! 

Key Features (all for FREE)
- Dark/Light mode themes
- Easy access to recently opened Google App Script Projects
- Access to helpful Code Snippets

Additional Features
- Links to purchase and download pre-built Code Templates


***Works best on Google Chrome
